name: ORS Non Association Report with Activities
description:
This report retrieves those Prisoners who have a current, active Non Association on their record, along with the details and location of the Non Association Prisoners. Report is over 6 tabs:
Located in Same Establishment, Same Est without Sections, Same Est by Location, All NA's, All without Sections and Activity locations.
Please Note: Trying to retrieve more than a weeks worth of activities may cause the report to fail, due to the amount of data to be returned.
ACC0043 - v5.0 Last Modified: 18/04/2024

dataset.name: Non Association A-F
dataset.query: dataset_base_ AS (SELECT AT_OFFENDER.OFFENDER_ID_DISPLAY, AT_OFFENDER.LAST_NAME, AT_OFFENDER.FIRST_NAME, AT_OFFENDER_NA_DETAILS.COMMENT_TEXT, AT_OFFENDER_NA_DETAILS.NS_EFFECTIVE_DATE, AT_OFFENDER_NA_DETAILS.NS_TYPE, AT_OFFENDER_NA_DETAILS.NS_REASON_CODE, AT_OFFENDERS_NA.OFFENDER_ID_DISPLAY AS NA_NOMS_NUMBER, AT_OFFENDERS_NA.LAST_NAME AS NA_LAST_NAME, AT_OFFENDERS_NA.FIRST_NAME AS NA_FIRST_NAME FROM OMS_OWNER.OFFENDERS AT_OFFENDER, OMS_OWNER.OFFENDER_BOOKINGS AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING, OMS_OWNER.AGENCY_LOCATIONS AT_OFFENDERS_LOCATIONS, OMS_OWNER.CASELOAD_AGENCY_LOCATIONS AT_CASELOAD_LOCATIONS, OMS_OWNER.OFFENDERS AT_OFFENDERS_NA, OMS_OWNER.OFFENDER_BOOKINGS AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING_NA, OMS_OWNER.OFFENDER_NA_DETAILS AT_OFFENDER_NA_DETAILS, OMS_OWNER.LIVING_UNITS AT_ALL_LIVING_UNITS, OMS_OWNER.OFFENDER_NON_ASSOCIATIONS AT_OFFENDER_NON_ASSOCIATIONS WHERE (AT_OFFENDER.OFFENDER_ID = AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.OFFENDER_ID) AND (AT_OFFENDERS_LOCATIONS.AGENCY_LOCATION_TYPE = 'INST') AND (AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.LIVING_UNIT_ID (+) = AT_ALL_LIVING_UNITS.LIVING_UNIT_ID) AND (AT_CASELOAD_LOCATIONS.AGY_LOC_ID = AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.AGY_LOC_ID) AND (AT_CASELOAD_LOCATIONS.AGY_LOC_ID = AT_OFFENDERS_LOCATIONS.AGY_LOC_ID (+)) AND (NOT AT_CASELOAD_LOCATIONS.AGY_LOC_ID IN ('OUT', 'TRN') AND NOT AT_CASELOAD_LOCATIONS.CASELOAD_ID IN ('ADMINC', 'CADM_I', 'MULTI')) AND (AT_OFFENDER_NON_ASSOCIATIONS.OFFENDER_ID (+) = AT_OFFENDER.ROOT_OFFENDER_ID) AND (AT_OFFENDERS_NA.ROOT_OFFENDER_ID = AT_OFFENDER_NA_DETAILS.NS_OFFENDER_ID) AND (AT_OFFENDER_NA_DETAILS.OFFENDER_ID = AT_OFFENDER_NON_ASSOCIATIONS.OFFENDER_ID AND AT_OFFENDER_NA_DETAILS.NS_OFFENDER_ID = AT_OFFENDER_NON_ASSOCIATIONS.NS_OFFENDER_ID) AND (AT_OFFENDERS_NA.OFFENDER_ID = AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING_NA.OFFENDER_ID) AND (AT_OFFENDER.LAST_NAME < 'G' AND (AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.ACTIVE_FLAG = 'Y') AND (AT_OFFENDERS_LOCATIONS.AGY_LOC_ID IN ((SELECT establishment_code FROM prompt_)) /* END Filter: Hierarchies/Establishment/''Establishment Code'' */) /* START Filter: Hierarchies/Establishment/''Establishment Code'' */ AND (AT_ALL_LIVING_UNITS.AGY_LOC_ID || '-' || AT_ALL_LIVING_UNITS.LEVEL_1_CODE IN ('All') OR 'All' IN ('All')) AND AT_OFFENDER_NA_DETAILS.NS_EXPIRY_DATE IS NULL AND AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING_NA.ACTIVE_FLAG = 'Y')), dataset_ AS (SELECT OFFENDER_ID_DISPLAY, LAST_NAME, FIRST_NAME, COMMENT_TEXT, NS_EFFECTIVE_DATE, NS_TYPE, NS_REASON_CODE, NA_NOMS_NUMBER, NA_LAST_NAME, NA_FIRST_NAME FROM dataset_base_)

dataset.name: Prisoner Location (5)
dataset.query: dataset_base_ AS (SELECT AT_OFFENDER.OFFENDER_ID_DISPLAY, SUBSTR(AT_AGENCY_INTERNAL_LOCATION_L4.DESCRIPTION, LENGTH(AT_AGENCY_INTERNAL_LOCATION_L4.AGY_LOC_ID) + 2, LENGTH(AT_AGENCY_INTERNAL_LOCATION_L4.DESCRIPTION)) AS UNIT_DESCRIPTION_4_SHORT, AT_ALL_LIVING_UNITS.AGY_LOC_ID || '-' || AT_ALL_LIVING_UNITS.LEVEL_1_CODE AS AGY_AND_LOCATION FROM OMS_OWNER.OFFENDERS AT_OFFENDER, OMS_OWNER.AGENCY_INTERNAL_LOCATIONS AT_AGENCY_INTERNAL_LOCATION_L4, OMS_OWNER.OFFENDER_BOOKINGS AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING, OMS_OWNER.AGENCY_LOCATIONS AT_OFFENDERS_LOCATIONS, OMS_OWNER.AGENCY_LOCATIONS AT_WING_ESTABLISHMENT, OMS_OWNER.CASELOAD_AGENCY_LOCATIONS AT_CASELOAD_LOCATIONS, USER_ACCESSIBLE_CASELOADS WING_CASELOAD_SECURITY, OMS_OWNER.LIVING_UNITS AT_ALL_LIVING_UNITS WHERE (AT_OFFENDER.OFFENDER_ID = AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.OFFENDER_ID) AND (AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.LIVING_UNIT_ID = AT_AGENCY_INTERNAL_LOCATION_L4.INTERNAL_LOCATION_ID) AND (AT_OFFENDERS_LOCATIONS.AGENCY_LOCATION_TYPE = 'INST') AND (AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.LIVING_UNIT_ID (+) = AT_ALL_LIVING_UNITS.LIVING_UNIT_ID) AND (AT_CASELOAD_LOCATIONS.AGY_LOC_ID = AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.AGY_LOC_ID) AND (AT_CASELOAD_LOCATIONS.AGY_LOC_ID = AT_OFFENDERS_LOCATIONS.AGY_LOC_ID (+)) AND (NOT AT_CASELOAD_LOCATIONS.AGY_LOC_ID IN ('OUT', 'TRN') AND NOT AT_CASELOAD_LOCATIONS.CASELOAD_ID IN ('ADMINC', 'CADM_I', 'MULTI')) AND (AT_AGENCY_INTERNAL_LOCATION_L4.AGY_LOC_ID = AT_WING_ESTABLISHMENT.AGY_LOC_ID) AND (AT_WING_ESTABLISHMENT.AGY_LOC_ID = WING_CASELOAD_SECURITY.CASELOAD_ID) AND (WING_CASELOAD_SECURITY.USERNAME = (SELECT username FROM context_)) AND ((AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.ACTIVE_FLAG = 'Y') AND (AT_OFFENDERS_LOCATIONS.AGY_LOC_ID IN ((SELECT establishment_code FROM prompt_)) /* END Filter: Hierarchies/Establishment/''Establishment Code'' */) /* START Filter: Hierarchies/Establishment/''Establishment Code'' */ AND (AT_ALL_LIVING_UNITS.AGY_LOC_ID || '-' || AT_ALL_LIVING_UNITS.LEVEL_1_CODE IN ('All') OR 'All' IN ('All')))), dataset_ AS (SELECT OFFENDER_ID_DISPLAY, UNIT_DESCRIPTION_4_SHORT, AGY_AND_LOCATION FROM dataset_base_)

dataset.name: Prisoner Activity
dataset.query: dataset_base_ AS (SELECT AT_OFFENDER.OFFENDER_ID_DISPLAY, AT_ACTIVITY_LOCATION.DESCRIPTION, AT_COURSE_ACTIVITIES.DESCRIPTION AS ACTIVITY_DESCRIPTION, AT_PROGRAM_PROFILES.SUSPENDED_FLAG FROM V_OFFENDER_COURSE_EVENTS, OMS_OWNER.COURSE_SCHEDULES AT_COURSE_SCHEDULES, OMS_OWNER.OFFENDER_PROGRAM_PROFILES AT_PROGRAM_PROFILES, OMS_OWNER.OFFENDERS AT_OFFENDER, OMS_OWNER.OFFENDER_BOOKINGS AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING, OMS_OWNER.AGENCY_LOCATIONS AT_OFFENDERS_LOCATIONS, OMS_OWNER.COURSE_ACTIVITIES AT_COURSE_ACTIVITIES, OMS_OWNER.CASELOAD_AGENCY_LOCATIONS AT_CASELOAD_LOCATIONS, OMS_OWNER.AGENCY_INTERNAL_LOCATIONS AT_ACTIVITY_LOCATION, OMS_OWNER.LIVING_UNITS AT_ALL_LIVING_UNITS WHERE (AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.OFFENDER_BOOK_ID = V_OFFENDER_COURSE_EVENTS.OFFENDER_BOOK_ID) AND (V_OFFENDER_COURSE_EVENTS.CRS_SCH_ID = AT_COURSE_SCHEDULES.CRS_SCH_ID AND V_OFFENDER_COURSE_EVENTS.CRS_ACTY_ID = AT_COURSE_SCHEDULES.CRS_ACTY_ID) AND (AT_COURSE_SCHEDULES.CRS_ACTY_ID = AT_COURSE_ACTIVITIES.CRS_ACTY_ID) AND (AT_COURSE_ACTIVITIES.INTERNAL_LOCATION_ID = AT_ACTIVITY_LOCATION.INTERNAL_LOCATION_ID) AND (AT_PROGRAM_PROFILES.OFF_PRGREF_ID = V_OFFENDER_COURSE_EVENTS.OFF_PRGREF_ID) AND (AT_OFFENDER.OFFENDER_ID = AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.OFFENDER_ID) AND (AT_OFFENDERS_LOCATIONS.AGENCY_LOCATION_TYPE = 'INST') AND (AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.LIVING_UNIT_ID (+) = AT_ALL_LIVING_UNITS.LIVING_UNIT_ID) AND (AT_CASELOAD_LOCATIONS.AGY_LOC_ID = AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.AGY_LOC_ID) AND (AT_CASELOAD_LOCATIONS.AGY_LOC_ID = AT_OFFENDERS_LOCATIONS.AGY_LOC_ID (+)) AND (NOT AT_CASELOAD_LOCATIONS.AGY_LOC_ID IN ('OUT', 'TRN') AND NOT AT_CASELOAD_LOCATIONS.CASELOAD_ID IN ('ADMINC', 'CADM_I', 'MULTI')) AND ((AT_OFFENDERS_LOCATIONS.AGY_LOC_ID IN ((SELECT establishment_code FROM prompt_)) /* END Filter: Hierarchies/Establishment/''Establishment Code'' */) /* START Filter: Hierarchies/Establishment/''Establishment Code'' */ AND (AT_OFFENDER_BOOKING.ACTIVE_FLAG = 'Y') AND (AT_ALL_LIVING_UNITS.AGY_LOC_ID || '-' || AT_ALL_LIVING_UNITS.LEVEL_1_CODE IN ('All') OR 'All' IN ('All')) AND V_OFFENDER_COURSE_EVENTS.EVENT_DATE BETWEEN TO_DATE('18-04-2024 00:00:00', 'DD-MM-YYYY HH24:MI:SS') AND TO_DATE('19-04-2024 00:00:00', 'DD-MM-YYYY HH24:MI:SS') AND CASE WHEN AT_COURSE_ACTIVITIES.SCHEDULE_END_DATE >= CURRENT_TIMESTAMP OR AT_COURSE_ACTIVITIES.SCHEDULE_END_DATE IS NULL THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N' END = 'Y')), dataset_ AS (SELECT OFFENDER_ID_DISPLAY, DESCRIPTION, ACTIVITY_DESCRIPTION, SUSPENDED_FLAG FROM dataset_base_)

filter.name: prefilter_
filter.query: prefilter_ AS (SELECT * FROM dataset_ WHERE V_SAME_PRISON = 1)
